<s> I'm curious about the use of tabs instead of spaces for indenting.  </s>
<s> I have always liked tabs (maily because of display in my editors).  </s>
<s> The tidy web page says "Tidy never outputs tabs".  </s>
<s> Is there a particular reason for this or just an option not implemented?  </s>
