<s> The number of columns for each tab stop varies from one system or program to another, Unix systems generally use 8, but other systems often use 4 or 5 columns.  </s>
<s> Many people like to use a smaller number of spaces, to maximize the space remaining before the right margin.  </s>
<s> In principle, an option could be added to use tabs, but this isn't a frequently requested option.  </s>
<s> Regards, -- Dave Raggett dsr@w3.org  </s>
